  /// @dev Two ways to pay the creation fee: send `ethFee()` wei with the call
  /// to lock 100% of `amount_`, or send 0 wei and have `tokenFeeBps()` deducted
  /// from `amount_` in the locked token itself.
  function createTokenLocker(
